AlphaGen Power LLC Rate Schedule FERC No. 2 Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service
AlphaGen Power LLC (???AlphaGen???) provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service (???Reactive Supply Service???) from a nominal 653 MW natural gas-fired facility located in Jackson, Michigan (the ???Facility???). The Facility is interconnected to the transmission system of Michigan Electric Transmission Company, LLC, which is administered by the Midcontinent Independent Transmission System Operator, Inc. (???MISO???). This Rate Schedule FERC No. 2 sets forth AlphaGen???s revenue requirement for the provision of Reactive Supply Service from the Facility consistent with Schedule 2 of the MISO Open Access Transmission, Energy, and Operating Reserve Markets Tariff. This Rate Schedule shall be effective as of March 1, 2014.
ANNUAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT: The annual revenue requirement is $1,175,000. The monthly charge is $97,916.67.
